She hoped that this bot would take her to the leader.  All she wanted 
to do was to talk to Quickstrike and find out what happened.  He 
didn't answer his commlink, and se had to find out what happened to 
commander.  She was more loyal to Quickstrike than Megatron.  She 
would follow Quickstrike to the inferno and back without a second 
thought.  Her programming demanded that she follow her commander.
